
This code was created to produce Ionospheric and Ground Maps as desribed in 
the publication: 

Methodology to estimate ionospheric scintillation risk maps and their contribution to position dilution of precision on the ground
Alexandra Koulouri, Nathan D. Smith, Bruno C. Vani, Ville Rimpilainen, Ivan Astin, Biagio Forte
https://arxiv.org/abs/1911.08229?context=physics

Please cite this publication or any other newer version if you use this code.
Please contact me (a.koulouri84@gmail.com) if you need help or you spot mistakes! Thank you!
